{"tid":1832425,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗官當道]區諾軒涉襲警案裁定表證成立 檢控主任遭辯方質疑「誤會咗法律」","createTime":"2020-01-21T07:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T07:42:44.000Z","uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b85583d640ce3a1662b6b993b310910c53111819","tid":1832425,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200121/large/1579584335_dfed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200121%2Flarge%2F1579584335_dfed.jpg&h=ccdc47e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主控官陳文慧。（楊思雅攝）<br />\n<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會前議員區諾軒被指以大聲公襲兩警，案件續審，區被裁定表證成立，聆訊押後至明早以待雙方結案陳詞。控辯雙方今早一度就多項法律議題提出爭拗，包括受襲警司高振邦的主診醫生能否以專家證人身份出庭、控方又能否在被告不出庭作供的情況下作結案陳詞等。辯方兩度揶揄控方，指控方「可能誤會咗法律」、「知（案例），似乎就冇實行」<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒於庭外強調，他由此至終沒有襲擊意圖。他指襲警罪刑罰很重，初犯亦可判監，但他最憂慮的是，見到警方和律政司對他的指控「講到好盡」，擔憂遭「砌生豬肉」。區又指，假若「連自己本身嘅清白都捍衛唔到，就唔係我一個人嘅事」，而是涉及立法會議員在衝突前線的監察功能會否遭受限制。"},{"pid":"ca81d352c13593c99dc639aa59d1e00a8deb20ca","tid":1832425,"uid":136186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HHqvc3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HHqvc3.gif&h=906d4624&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"540996bf10f038c4a2ba1b6aa84c50e2f546c651","tid":1832425,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:13:22.000Z","msg":"點知隻狗聽力短暫受損係因為大聲公定側邊d狗大叫引致？"},{"pid":"8517b586eb04c5db42dd3819f4427b25e36e6c29","tid":1832425,"uid":270307,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca81d352c13593c99dc639aa59d1e00a8deb20ca","tid":1832425,"uid":136186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HHqvc3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HHqvc3.gif&h=906d4624&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECKUkd4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECKUkd4.gif&h=98264159&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"212a4b037e7c8cdab5a95ea13027a479dfa2f67e","tid":1832425,"uid":143400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQiU4EW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQiU4EW.gif&h=6892f4d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3e4bfb1c98a67a2e108540d2c5b7a12ee24795d","tid":1832425,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"表證成立在刑事案中常見，律師謝連忠指出只要控方的證據及證人口供具某程度的完整性，表面看來並非不可靠、不齊全或缺乏根據，法庭一般都會作出表證成立裁決，卻不代表被告被裁定罪成，不少被告被裁定表證成立，但審訊完畢後會被判無罪。<br />\n不少辯護律師，喜歡採用指示當事人不自辯的策略，以免其自辯供詞有矛盾之處，反而削弱勝算。辯護策略不一定要證明被告無罪，只要證明控方的證據存有疑點，在「疑點利益歸於被告」的大前提下，被告便可獲判無罪"},{"pid":"1199ee8a660efd4c6b6e461b3f2602cdbf0e433f","tid":1832425,"uid":28938,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:33:35.000Z","msg":"留案底會令人生變得更精彩.jpg <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐返幾個月啦你個死矮仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5617105b1c9dec60ba0b54c73ea4ae2b9822cb7","tid":1832425,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:38:56.000Z","msg":"想話佢慘，但又覺得係因果循環<br />\n當年hktv示威你甘願做第二梯隊幫政府降溫<br />\n到宜家先發現原來法律係保護唔到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過肯棄暗投明都算係咁"},{"pid":"54c91dedce3fbb468e41a78e4510f45e60e7c384","tid":1832425,"uid":61330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"Over my dead body"},{"pid":"bf76b606edb96aa17d924c573ba115a46a39a30a","tid":1832425,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5617105b1c9dec60ba0b54c73ea4ae2b9822cb7","tid":1832425,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-2